<h5 id="subject_809891">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=85898.msg809891#msg809891" rel="nofollow">[扩展数据][授权转载] Lodoss 战役设定数据：角色，物品，怪物</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_809891'));undefined;">繁</a>
